FT  27 OCT 94 / UK Company News: Butte revises loss
Butte Mining's audited results for the year to June 30 showed pre-tax losses
of Pounds 351,000, giving losses per share of 0.15p. The preliminary
announcement gave pre-tax losses of Pounds 436,000.
The improvement comes as a result of the company writing back certain
provisions no longer necessary.
